{"data":{"metadata":{"authors":{},"created_at":1645838554000,"identifier":"/docs/stores/htmlmode","modified_at":1645838554000,"sections":[{"identifier":"htmlmode","level":1,"text":"htmlmode"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"built-in-shortcuts","level":2,"text":"Built-In Shortcuts"},{"identifier":"compatibility","level":2,"text":"Compatibility"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"htmlmode-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Code,\n        Heading,\n        Text,\n        htmlmode,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n\n    const mode_store = htmlmode();\n</script>\n\n<Heading>Application Theme Mode</Heading>\n\n<Text>\n    <Code>&lt;html data-mode&gt;</Code>: <Code>\n        \"{$mode_store}\"\n    </Code>\n</Text>","syntax":"svelte","title":"htmlmode Preview"},{"identifier":"htmlmode-built-in-shortcuts","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Code,\n        Heading,\n        Text,\n        htmldark,\n        htmllight,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n\n    const dark_store = htmldark();\n    const light_store = htmllight();\n</script>\n\n<Heading>Application Theme Mode</Heading>\n\n<Text>\n    <Code>&lt;html data-mode=\"dark\"&gt;</Code>: <Code>\n        {$dark_store}\n    </Code>\n</Text>\n\n<Text>\n    <Code>&lt;html data-mode=\"light\"&gt;</Code>: <Code>\n        {$light_store}\n    </Code>\n</Text>","syntax":"svelte","title":"htmlmode Built-In Shortcuts"}],"title":"htmlmode"},"text":"htmlmode NOTE : Introduced feature in v0.2.3. WARNING : This feature was renamed from htmlpalette to htmlmode in v0.6.0 . USAGE : This feature can be demonstrated by clicking the Theme Toggle button in the top navigation. htmlmode is a Svelte Store , which is bound to <html data-mode=\"XXX\"> and updates whenever that attribute is changed. Defaulting to an empty string (\"\") if not set. <script> import { Code, Heading, Text, htmlmode, } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\"; const mode_store = htmlmode(); </script> <Heading>Application Theme Mode</Heading> <Text> <Code>&lt;html data-mode&gt;</Code>: <Code> \"{$mode_store}\" </Code> </Text> Imports import { htmlmode, htmldark, htmllight, } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\"; Built-In Shortcuts NOTE : Introduced feature in v0.6.0. The htmlmode Store also comes with two readonly preconfigured shortcut Stores, htmldark and htmllight. <script> import { Code, Heading, Text, htmldark, htmllight, } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\"; const dark_store = htmldark(); const light_store = htmllight(); </script> <Heading>Application Theme Mode</Heading> <Text> <Code>&lt;html data-mode=\"dark\"&gt;</Code>: <Code> {$dark_store} </Code> </Text> <Text> <Code>&lt;html data-mode=\"light\"&gt;</Code>: <Code> {$light_store} </Code> </Text> Compatibility The Store is dependent on MutationObserver . So if you're rendering on the server, it'll always return an empty string (\"\"). ","references":{"custom_properties":{},"events":{},"properties":{},"slots":{}},"render":"<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Introduced feature in <code>v0.2.3</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"alert\">\n<p><strong>WARNING</strong>: This feature was renamed from <code>htmlpalette</code> to <code>htmlmode</code> in <a href=\"../migrations/0.5.x-to-0.6.x\" svelte:prefetch=\"true\"><code>v0.6.0</code></a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"informative\">\n<p><strong>USAGE</strong>: This feature can be demonstrated by clicking the <strong>Theme Toggle</strong> button in the top navigation.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><code>htmlmode</code> is a <a href=\"https://svelte.dev/docs#svelte_store\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Svelte Store</a>, which is bound to <code>&lt;html data-mode=&quot;XXX&quot;&gt;</code> and updates whenever that attribute is changed. Defaulting to an empty string (<code>&quot;&quot;</code>) if not set.</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"htmlmode-preview\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        Code<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Heading<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        Text<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        htmlmode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> mode_store <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">htmlmode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Heading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Application Theme Mode<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Heading</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&lt;\">&amp;lt;</span>html data-mode<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&gt;\">&amp;gt;</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        \"<span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$mode_store<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\"\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-javascript\" data-identifier=\"htmlmode-imports\" data-mode=\"default\" data-syntax=\"javascript\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    htmlmode<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    htmldark<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    htmllight<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><h2 id=\"built-in-shortcuts\">Built-In Shortcuts</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: Introduced feature in <code>v0.6.0</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <code>htmlmode</code> Store also comes with two <strong>readonly</strong> preconfigured shortcut Stores, <code>htmldark</code> and <code>htmllight</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"highlight language-svelte\" data-identifier=\"htmlmode-built-in-shortcuts\" data-mode=\"repl\" data-syntax=\"svelte\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\