lass=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&lt;\">&amp;lt;</span>html data-mode=\"dark\"<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&gt;\">&amp;gt;</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$dark_store<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&lt;\">&amp;lt;</span>html data-mode=\"light\"<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"&gt;\">&amp;gt;</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>$light_store<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>Text</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"compatibility\">Compatibility</h2>\n<p>The Store is dependent on <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a>. So if you're rendering on the server, it'll always return an empty string (<code>&quot;&quot;</code>).</p>\n"}}